{"tid":441119,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「閻奕格之難」閻奕格出新碟 譚校長勁讚：新一輩歌手中最掂","createTime":"2017-10-19T11:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T09:56:25.000Z","uid":60584,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8fff9a44ff9336e976e1ffe36765cfcaca1e7abd","tid":441119,"uid":60584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57352035&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57352035%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171019&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7lzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c717a9b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57352035%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171019&h=ddbcba1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57352035&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171019</a><br />\n<br />\n閻奕格喺七年前以踢館參賽者身份參加台北嘅「超級星光大道」闖出名堂，可惜之後經歷抑鬱，令開始起飛事業停下來，到14年復出。<br />\n<br />\n今日佢喺九展舉行記招，宣佈聽日全亞洲同步發行首張專輯《我有我自己》，為佢填寫第一首粤語歌嘅黃偉文同之前合作過舞台劇嘅呂良偉、謝天華、鄭丹瑞等預錄祝賀片段，而陳淑芬則親自送上紫色馬擺設，當聽到陳淑芬讚美後，閻奕格感動眼濕，另外校長譚詠麟扮聲扮長途電話祝賀，起初閻奕格完全估不到係邊個，最後估中係校長後，譚校長即時現身台上，更送上一把巨型扇，並寫上「大紅」兩字，譚校長話：「放心，呢把唔係大葵扇，喺事業努力多幾年先。」之後大會再宣佈閻奕格將於12月12日假九展Star Hall開騷，譚校長仲預祝佢下一次就係「紅館開騷」。<br />\n<br />\n譚校長話閻奕格係新一輩歌手中最掂，唱任何年代粤語、國語同英文歌都得，可以用萬能形容，有能力重燃香港樂壇盛勢，而譚校長亦好奇問閻奕格點解咁耐先出碟，閻奕格話：「比賽後我返咗美國讀書，之後身體出現問題休息咗兩三年，當你曾經失去舞台再重新擁有會更珍惜。」佢亦感激譚校長幾年前邀請佢做溫拿演唱會嘉賓，令佢首次踏足紅館。首次推出專輯，閻奕格特別感激當佢肥至70公斤走晒樣時，仍有人對自己不離不棄，支持佢走出低谷。今次在港開騷，閻奕格好開心可以唱出自己喜歡嘅經典廣東歌，將自己心路歷程同大家分享。譚校長被問到早前同李克勤兩家人遊台灣，佢大方承認有去玩，問到係咪阿囝放假一齊去？佢話：「阿囝嗰啲係舊相。」"},{"pid":"9cf1970fcfb332ace22c05d64c482f59818bb691","tid":441119,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"今次仆街了<br />\n好搞唔搞搞格格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6239a1462110d3ccad089ebb10f518a4fb70a65","tid":441119,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"完了吧"},{"pid":"a42f9f40499670bcf8eca688026c33e6e6fc1f36","tid":441119,"uid":25125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"譚校長即時現身台上，更送上一把巨型扇，並寫上「大紅」兩字<br />\n<br />\n譚校長仲預祝佢下一次就係「紅館開騷」"},{"pid":"ba5799292626952924ae2ef018dae5fa1ebab5ba","tid":441119,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"格格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d984d138dc4f93af175f01626bcb5f60d0659683","tid":441119,"uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"佢之前燈過咩人？"},{"pid":"b365a1751acf629b16459c1349c00e5e561b8a77","tid":441119,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe0e607365ef3251a9eff8177a101dd1294b663","tid":441119,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:25:17.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b49ffacfbf1055a2c87aa337bfd0b13b9fad823","tid":441119,"uid":25125,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢之前燈過咩人？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/164378_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com